    <item>
      <title>泰国计划削减游客的无签证住宿至30天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/thailand-mulls-cutting-tourists-visa-free-stay-to-30-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据旅游业和体育部长Sorawong Thienthong的说法，泰国计划使外国游客能够在没有签证的情况下停留的天数减少到30天，因为东南亚国家打击旅行者，利用豁免来从事非法业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/thailand-mulls-cutting-tourists-visa-free-stay-to-30-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 01:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金在中东紧张局势上记录，美国经济的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/gold-xausd-holds-near-3-000-as-us-data-adds-to-concerns-over-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势的升级强调了其避风港的吸引力，因此黄金上升到每盎司3,017美元以上的高度高于$ 3,017，并且投资者权衡了对美国经济的促进数据的权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/gold-xausd-holds-near-3-000-as-us-data-adds-to-concerns-over-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:23:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
